{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"402","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"再生能源行嗎？ 民間盤點十大綠能假新聞 闢謠看這篇","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>假新聞滿天飛，與綠能有關的更是不勝枚舉。拿大錢給外商蓋離岸風機，台灣人是「盤子」？風機在轉電錶卻沒電？太陽能板有毒？光電廠商為施工抽乾埤塘水？夏天沒風、冬天沒光，再生能源不可行？2018年步入尾聲，今（26）台灣再生能源推動聯盟選出年度十大關鍵綠能假新聞，並加以澄清。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>台灣再生能源推動聯盟理事長高茹萍指出，假新聞影響民眾甚廣，從今年公投通過16案「以核養綠」就可看出，民眾對綠能信心不足而選擇延後2025非核家園時程。聯盟也邀立委陳曼麗、映發科技、聯合再生能源公司、台灣瑞曼迪斯公司等業界出席記者會共同澄清。</p>\n\n<p class='align-center' style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'><a data-rapid_p='10' data-track='photo-click' href='https://www.flickr.com/photos/teia/46416967232/in/photostream' id='yui_3_11_0_3_1545805258634_946' style='color: rgb(95, 151, 8); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; text-decoration-line: none;' target='_blank'><img alt='1226-2' border='0' data-thumbdata='' height='408' id='yui_3_11_0_3_1545805258634_950' src='https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4912/46416967232_aee95619e9_b.jpg' style='padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;' width='753' /></a></p>\n\n<h3 style='line-height: 1.477; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.4em; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.05em; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; color: rgb(104, 166, 23);'>太陽能板有毒？</h3>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>對於太陽能板很毒的說法，映發科技總經理李喆龍指出，太陽能板的模組其實與平板差不多。「3C歸類在可回收，為何太陽能板不可回收？」李喆龍解釋，太陽能板上是玻璃，想像平板拿去清洗會不會有塗料的問題，這是相同的道理，太陽能板卻被污名化。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>他說，太陽能板的製程僅3C的一半，如果3C是環保產品，為何大家都說太陽能板有毒？太陽能板製程的廢液與晶圓一樣都可回收、可管制。</p>\n\n<h3 style='line-height: 1.477; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.4em; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.05em; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; color: rgb(104, 166, 23);'>「夏天無風、冬天無光」，風能、太陽能無用？</h3>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>對此，李喆龍表示，一年四季都會有風，也會有光。風、光可以互相補足用電需求，不能只看單一選項。</p>\n\n<h3 style='line-height: 1.477; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.4em; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.05em; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; color: rgb(104, 166, 23);'>八一五停電原因？非缺電！</h3>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>李喆龍指出，八一五停電是天燃氣電動閥誤關所致，體現出「能源集中」的風險。現在全世界已經在朝分散式能源前進，集中式能源的風險卻沒有在台灣好好檢討，誤傳成缺電，這是很危險的事。</p>\n\n<div class='align-center' style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>\n<figure class='image' style='text-align: inherit; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-radius: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; width: 1024px;'><a data-rapid_p='26' data-track='photo-click' href='https://www.flickr.com/photos/teia/45744391534/in/photostream' id='yui_3_11_0_3_1545804836659_991' style='color: rgb(95, 151, 8); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; text-decoration-line: none;' target='_blank'><img alt='映發科技總經理李喆龍澄清光電有毒、815停電是缺電等消息。攝影：陳文姿' border='0' data-thumbdata='' height='631' id='yui_3_11_0_3_1545804836659_990' src='https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7872/45744391534_3cf2816336_b.jpg' style='padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; display: block;' width='1024' /></a>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<figcaption style='text-align: left; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 1em 0.6em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;'>映發科技總經理李喆龍澄清光電有毒、815停電是缺電等消息。攝影：陳文姿</figcaption>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;'>&nbsp;</p>\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n<h3 style='line-height: 1.477; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.4em; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.05em; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; color: rgb(104, 166, 23);'>太陽能板不能回收？</h3>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>瑞曼迪斯總經理戴英傑，以德國最大環保公司、長期在台經營的經驗指出，歐洲的太陽能板回收技術上已從90%提升到96%，主要問題不在技術，而是近年矽價格不好。這問題與早期回收寶特瓶很貴類似，初期需要政府補助，但如今寶特瓶回收已能自給自足。</p>\n\n<h3 style='line-height: 1.477; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.4em; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.05em; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; color: rgb(104, 166, 23);'>離岸風力好貴 陸域風機不發電&nbsp;台灣政府是盤子？</h3>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>高茹萍指出，離岸風電是全新產業，風電開發商要在缺乏風力、水文資料的台灣海峽上蓋風機，要付出很多社會溝通成本、基礎建設、人員訓練。政府要求離岸風電商擔負在地生產製造的國產化責任，投資在離岸風機上的錢不全是給開發商，很多都是用在投資台灣的綠能產業鏈。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>高茹萍解釋，歐洲離岸風電剛開始的時候也很貴，現在市場成熟了，所以價格才能下降。台灣現在開始投資，未來就能享受這樣降價的好處。現在不付出，以後就要承擔愈來愈貴的能源價格。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>對於民眾拍到陸域風機在運轉卻不發電的新聞，高茹萍也澄清，民眾拍的風機屬鹿威公司，但電錶卻是台電的，這是張冠李戴。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>台電使用Vestas機型要風速大於4m/s才運轉。事實上，冬天的風力可以減少燃煤的使用，對於減少空污很有幫助。</p>\n\n<div class='align-center' style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: center; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>\n<figure class='image' style='text-align: inherit; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; border-color: initial; border-radius: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; max-width: 100%; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; width: 1024px;'><a data-rapid_p='2' data-track='photo-click' href='https://www.flickr.com/photos/teia/45744391314/in/photostream' id='yui_3_11_0_3_1545804836659_945' style='color: rgb(95, 151, 8); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; text-decoration-line: none;' target='_blank'><img alt='台灣再生能源推動聯盟與立委陳曼麗、光電業者、回收商共同召開記者會，澄清2018年綠電假新聞。攝影：陳文姿' border='0' data-thumbdata='' height='546' id='yui_3_11_0_3_1545804836659_944' src='https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4847/45744391314_3eb1d845d0_b.jpg' style='padding: 0px; margin: 0px auto; border-width: 0px; border-style: initial; outline: 0px; vertical-align: bottom; max-width: 100%; height: auto; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; display: block;' width='1024' /></a>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<figcaption style='text-align: left; margin: 0px; padding: 10px 1em 0.6em; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;'>台灣再生能源推動聯盟與立委陳曼麗、光電業者、回收商共同召開記者會，澄清2018年綠電假新聞。攝影：陳文姿</figcaption>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit;'>&nbsp;</p>\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n<h3 style='line-height: 1.477; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.4em; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.05em; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; color: rgb(104, 166, 23);'>太陽能板的製造很耗能？&nbsp;&nbsp;</h3>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>陳曼麗以綠色和平《中國光伏產業清潔研究報告》指出，太陽能板發電約1.3年就可以抵銷生產過程的耗能，但太陽能卻可以使用25年，等於20幾年都是在賺錢。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>陳曼麗也澄清，太陽能的清洗只要用清水即可，請大家不要再誤傳。</p>\n\n<h3 style='line-height: 1.477; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 1.4em; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.05em; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-rendering: optimizeSpeed; color: rgb(104, 166, 23);'>埤塘光電故意抽乾水？</h3>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>針對去年底桃園埤塘進行太陽能光電工程，竟「為了工程」抽乾埤塘池水的新聞，該案的光電系統商、聯合再生能源的專案經理林家政解釋，水利固定在每年年底灌溉告一段落時進行歲修，公司利用這段期間施工。排水並非是為了光電工程。他強調，工程作業經農委會、桃園市政府、水利會審查監督，並在灌溉期前恢復蓄水，沒有對農民造成影響。</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style='margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 19.2px; line-height: 2; font-family: Helvetica, &quot;Noto Sans CJK TC&quot;, &quot;PingFang TC&quot;, &quot;Heiti TC&quot;, 微軟正黑體, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);'>資料來源：https://e-info.org.tw/node/215703</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2019-01-07","clk_count":"174"}},"__N_SSG":true}